title: Any guesses?
content:
![](http://web.archive.org/web/20131015175750im_/http:/typophile.com/files/type_6649.gif)
  
I feel I should know this one, but I can't seem to find it in my type books. Any guesses?
author: Corey Holms

comments.content: I can't think of anything off the top of my head, but if you just need this re-created it would be easy enough to do in Illustrator.

That's what I eventually did.  
I could swear that this is a commercially available typeface that I've seen before... I don't want to rip anyone off or anything, I was perfectly willing to buy the typeface were it available.

Thanks for the suggestion!
